{
  "texts": [
    "To preserve the UK focus of the study, we also utilized the geography field from the meta-data.",
    "Articles mentioning any of the following terms in geography -London, England, United Kingdom, Ireland, Scotland, Wales, UK, and Ukraine were considered geographically related articles.",
    "We considered the country Ukraine as relevant geographically in order to include in the analysis the relationship between the latest crisis talk and the Ukraine war.",
    "The final corpus consists of 31,769 articles and Table 1 shows its statistics.",
    "The corpus retrieved using the 16 search keywords related to energy crisis talk contained irrelevant articles as well."
  ]
}